{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01HJLs5tWvsDLVgL2vty1Qd3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_019ZkhVWHwTgakqVXrTzAG4D","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Migrate interfaces and utility files","prompt":"You need to REWRITE the following Java files in-place at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_2/output to remove all Quarkus/CDI specific annotations and replace with plain Java annotations. Use the Write tool for each file.\n\n## 1. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/RuntimeMode.java\nReplace with a plain Java annotation (no CDI Qualifier):\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface RuntimeMode {\n    String value() default \"\";\n}\n```\n\n## 2. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/TradeEJB.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface TradeEJB {\n}\n```\n\n## 3. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/TradeJDBC.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface TradeJDBC {\n}\n```\n\n## 4. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/TradeSession2Direct.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface TradeSession2Direct {\n}\n```\n\n## 5. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/Trace.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface Trace {\n}\n```\n\n## 6. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/QuotePriceChange.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface QuotePriceChange {\n}\n```\n\n## 7. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/MarketSummaryUpdate.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface MarketSummaryUpdate {\n}\n```\n\n## 8. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/TradeRunTimeModeLiteral.java\nReplace with a simplified class (no CDI AnnotationLiteral):\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util;\n\npublic class TradeRunTimeModeLiteral {\n    private final String value;\n    \n    public TradeRunTimeModeLiteral(String value) {\n        this.value = value;\n    }\n    \n    public String value() {\n        return value;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 9. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/RecentQuotePriceChangeList.java\nRead the current file first, then replace CDI annotations with Spring. The key pattern is:\n- Replace @ApplicationScoped with @Service\n- Replace @Inject Event with @Autowired ApplicationEventPublisher (or remove the event firing if it's just cosmetic)\n- Replace jakarta.enterprise imports with Spring imports\n\nRead this file first to see its current content, then rewrite it.\n\nWrite ALL these files using the Write tool. Read the files that need inspection first.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":470,"cache_read_input_tokens":132497,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":470,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":5104},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0a2ab8cf-d9b3-4fb3-875c-ac24a464972f","uuid":"326f32ea-9816-4664-bc3b-76ad157747f8"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01HJLs5tWvsDLVgL2vty1Qd3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_014E5cqqH4NQFf1TiQASdPng","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Migrate service layer files","prompt":"You need to REWRITE the following Java service files in-place at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_2/output to migrate from Quarkus CDI to Spring Boot. Use the Read tool to read each file first, then use the Write tool to write the migrated version.\n\nREAD EACH FILE BEFORE WRITING.\n\n## 1. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/TradeSLSBBean.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service` and add `@Primary`\n- Replace `@Inject EntityManager` with `@PersistenceContext EntityManager`\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` with `org.springframework.stereotype.Service`\n- Replace `jakarta.inject.Inject` with `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n- Replace `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n- Remove CDI qualifier annotations (@Default, @TradeEJB, @RuntimeMode, @Trace)\n- Remove `jakarta.enterprise.event.Event` and `@MarketSummaryUpdate` event, replace with nothing (just remove event firing)\n- Remove `@Any Instance<TradeServices>` usage - replace with direct @Autowired\n- Keep the `@Transactional` annotation on class\n- Keep all business logic unchanged\n\n## 2. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/MarketSummarySingleton.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service`\n- Replace `@Inject EntityManager` with `@PersistenceContext EntityManager` \n- Replace `io.quarkus.scheduler.Scheduled` with `org.springframework.scheduling.annotation.Scheduled`\n- Change `@Scheduled(every = \"20s\")` to `@Scheduled(fixedRate = 20000)`\n- Remove CDI `Event<String>` and `@MarketSummaryUpdate` - just remove the event firing lines\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise` imports with Spring imports\n- Replace `jakarta.inject.Inject` with `@Autowired`\n\n## 3. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/session2direct/DirectSLSBBean.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service(\"directSLSBBean\")`\n- Remove `@TradeSession2Direct`, `@RuntimeMode`, `@Trace` annotations\n- Replace `@Inject @TradeJDBC TradeServices tradeDirect` with `@Autowired @Qualifier(\"tradeDirect\") TradeServices tradeDirect`\n- Replace `@Inject AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter` with `@Autowired`\n- Replace `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n- Replace all `jakarta.enterprise` and `jakarta.inject` imports with Spring imports\n- Add `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier;`\n\n## 4. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrder.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@Dependent` with `@Component` and `@Scope(\"prototype\")`\n- Remove CDI `@Any Instance<TradeServices>` - replace constructor with simple @Autowired TradeServices\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise` and `jakarta.inject` imports with Spring imports\n- Add `import org.springframework.context.annotation.Scope;`\n- Change constructor to use @Autowired TradeServices directly (no Instance/select pattern)\n\n## 5. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@RequestScoped` with `@Service`\n- Remove `@VirtualThreads` and `io.quarkus.virtual.threads.VirtualThreads` import\n- Replace `@Inject ExecutorService` with a simple `java.util.concurrent.Executors.newCachedThreadPool()` field\n- Replace `@Inject AsyncScheduledOrder` with `@Autowired`\n- Replace all `jakarta` imports with Spring imports\n\n## 6. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/AsyncOrderSubmitter.java\nRead first, then migrate similarly to AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.\n\n## 7. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/AsyncOrder.java\nRead first, then migrate similarly to AsyncScheduledOrder.\n\nWrite ALL files using the Write tool.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":470,"cache_read_input_tokens":132497,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":470,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":5104},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0a2ab8cf-d9b3-4fb3-875c-ac24a464972f","uuid":"0dbaeb86-4086-4d6a-bb64-63286faf666e"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01HJLs5tWvsDLVgL2vty1Qd3","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_01XF3hCf7peknkWsRWZkLDyd","name":"Task","input":{"description":"Migrate TradeDirect and messaging","prompt":"You need to REWRITE the following Java files in-place at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_2/output to migrate from Quarkus CDI to Spring Boot. Use the Read tool to read each file first, then use the Write tool to write the migrated version.\n\nREAD EACH FILE BEFORE WRITING. Preserve all business logic.\n\n## 1. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/TradeDirect.java\nThis is the most complex file. Key changes:\n- Replace `@Dependent` with `@Service(\"tradeDirect\")` and add `@Scope(\"prototype\")`\n- Remove `@TradeJDBC`, `@RuntimeMode(\"Direct (JDBC)\")`, `@Trace` annotations\n- Replace `@Inject private DataSource datasource` with `@Autowired private DataSource datasource`\n- REMOVE `@Inject private UserTransaction txn` entirely. Remove the `import jakarta.transaction.UserTransaction;`\n- REMOVE `import io.quarkus.narayana.jta.QuarkusTransaction;`\n- Replace `@Inject RecentQuotePriceChangeList` with `@Autowired`\n- Replace `@Inject AsyncOrderSubmitter` with `@Autowired`\n- Replace `@Inject @MarketSummaryUpdate Event<String> mkSummaryUpdateEvent` with NOTHING (remove the field)\n- Replace `@Inject MessageProducerService messageProducer` with `@Autowired`\n- In the `buy()` method: Replace `txn.begin()` / `txn.commit()` / `txn.rollback()` with setting `conn.setAutoCommit(false)` and using `conn.commit()` / `conn.rollback()`. Set `inGlobalTxn = false` where `txn.begin()` was.\n- In the `sell()` method: Same as buy - remove txn usage, use connection-level transactions\n- Remove `mkSummaryUpdateEvent.fireAsync(...)` calls\n- Replace all `jakarta.enterprise`, `jakarta.inject` imports with Spring imports\n- Add `import org.springframework.stereotype.Service;` and `import org.springframework.context.annotation.Scope;` and `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;`\n- Keep `import javax.sql.DataSource;` (this is standard Java)\n- Keep `import jakarta.annotation.Resource;` only if needed, otherwise remove\n- Remove `import jakarta.annotation.Resource;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.enterprise.context.Dependent;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.enterprise.event.Event;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.enterprise.event.NotificationOptions;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.inject.Inject;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.transaction.UserTransaction;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.validation.constraints.NotNull;`\n\nFor the buy/sell transaction handling, change the pattern from:\n```java\nif (!inSession && orderProcessingMode == TradeConfig.ASYNCH_2PHASE) {\n    txn.begin();\n    setInGlobalTxn(true);\n}\n```\nTo:\n```java\n// 2-phase not supported in Spring - use connection-level transactions\n```\nAnd remove:\n```java\nif (getInGlobalTxn()) {\n    txn.commit();\n    setInGlobalTxn(false);\n}\n```\nReplace with:\n```java\ncommit(conn);\n```\nSimilarly for rollback.\n\n## 2. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/TradeDirectDBUtils.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service`\n- Replace `@Inject AgroalDataSource datasource` with `@Autowired DataSource datasource`\n- Remove `import io.agroal.api.AgroalDataSource;`\n- Replace `@Inject @TradeJDBC TradeServices ts` with `@Autowired @Qualifier(\"tradeDirect\") TradeServices ts`\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` with `org.springframework.stereotype.Service`\n- Replace `jakarta.inject.Inject` with `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n- Add `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier;`\n\n## 3. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/MessageProducerService.java\nReplace SmallRye Reactive Messaging with Spring ApplicationEventPublisher:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.messaging;\n\nimport java.math.BigDecimal;\n\nimport org.springframework.context.ApplicationEventPublisher;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\n\nimport com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.Log;\n\n@Service\npublic class MessageProducerService {\n\n    private final ApplicationEventPublisher eventPublisher;\n\n    public MessageProducerService(ApplicationEventPublisher eventPublisher) {\n        this.eventPublisher = eventPublisher;\n    }\n\n    public void queueOrderForProcessing(Integer orderID, boolean twoPhase) {\n        OrderMessage message = OrderMessage.newOrder(orderID, twoPhase);\n        Log.trace(\"MessageProducerService:queueOrderForProcessing - sending order \" + orderID);\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(message);\n    }\n\n    public void sendBrokerPing(String text) {\n        OrderMessage message = OrderMessage.ping(text);\n        Log.trace(\"MessageProducerService:sendBrokerPing - sending ping\");\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(message);\n    }\n\n    public void publishQuoteUpdate(String symbol, BigDecimal newPrice, BigDecimal oldPrice) {\n        QuoteUpdateMessage message = QuoteUpdateMessage.quoteUpdate(symbol, newPrice, oldPrice);\n        Log.trace(\"MessageProducerService:publishQuoteUpdate - publishing update for \" + symbol);\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(message);\n    }\n\n    public void publishQuotePriceChange(String symbol, String company, BigDecimal price,\n            BigDecimal oldPrice, BigDecimal open, BigDecimal low, BigDecimal high,\n            double volume, BigDecimal changeFactor, double sharesTraded) {\n        QuoteUpdateMessage message = QuoteUpdateMessage.quoteUpdate(symbol, price, oldPrice);\n        message.setCompany(company);\n        message.setOpen(open);\n        message.setLow(low);\n        message.setHigh(high);\n        message.setVolume(volume);\n        message.setChangeFactor(changeFactor);\n        message.setSharesTraded(sharesTraded);\n        Log.trace(\"MessageProducerService:publishQuotePriceChange - publishing update for \" + symbol);\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(message);\n    }\n\n    public void sendStreamerPing(String text) {\n        QuoteUpdateMessage message = QuoteUpdateMessage.ping(text);\n        Log.trace(\"MessageProducerService:sendStreamerPing - sending ping\");\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(message);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 4. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTBroker3MDB.java\nReplace @Incoming with Spring @EventListener:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service`\n- Replace `@Incoming(\"trade-broker-queue\")` with `@EventListener`\n- Replace `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n- Remove `org.eclipse.microprofile.reactive.messaging.Incoming`\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise` and `jakarta.inject` imports with Spring imports\n- Keep @PostConstruct (use `jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct`)\n\n## 5. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTStreamer3MDB.java\nSame pattern as DTBroker3MDB:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service`\n- Replace `@Incoming(\"trade-streamer-topic\")` with `@EventListener`\n- Remove MicroProfile imports\n\n## 6. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/startup/DatabasePopulator.java\nRead first, then:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n- Replace `@Inject EntityManager` with `@PersistenceContext EntityManager`\n- Replace `@ConfigProperty(name = \"trade.db.populate.on.startup\")` with `@Value(\"${trade.db.populate.on.startup:true}\")`\n- Replace `void onStart(@Observes StartupEvent ev)` with `@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent.class) public void onStart()`\n- Remove `io.quarkus.runtime.StartupEvent` import, add `org.springframework.boot.context.event.ApplicationReadyEvent` and `org.springframework.context.event.EventListener`\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise` imports with Spring imports\n\nWrite ALL files completely using the Write tool.","subagent_type":"general-purpose"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":470,"cache_read_input_tokens":132497,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":470,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":5104},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0a2ab8cf-d9b3-4fb3-875c-ac24a464972f","uuid":"24540806-0667-4f4f-9145-39137b1b9bb3"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You need to REWRITE the following Java files in-place at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_2/output to remove all Quarkus/CDI specific annotations and replace with plain Java annotations. Use the Write tool for each file.\n\n## 1. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/RuntimeMode.java\nReplace with a plain Java annotation (no CDI Qualifier):\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface RuntimeMode {\n    String value() default \"\";\n}\n```\n\n## 2. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/TradeEJB.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface TradeEJB {\n}\n```\n\n## 3. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/TradeJDBC.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface TradeJDBC {\n}\n```\n\n## 4. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/TradeSession2Direct.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface TradeSession2Direct {\n}\n```\n\n## 5. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/Trace.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface Trace {\n}\n```\n\n## 6. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/QuotePriceChange.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface QuotePriceChange {\n}\n```\n\n## 7. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/interfaces/MarketSummaryUpdate.java\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.interfaces;\nimport java.lang.annotation.ElementType;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Retention;\nimport java.lang.annotation.RetentionPolicy;\nimport java.lang.annotation.Target;\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Target({ElementType.TYPE, ElementType.METHOD, ElementType.FIELD})\npublic @interface MarketSummaryUpdate {\n}\n```\n\n## 8. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/TradeRunTimeModeLiteral.java\nReplace with a simplified class (no CDI AnnotationLiteral):\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util;\n\npublic class TradeRunTimeModeLiteral {\n    private final String value;\n    \n    public TradeRunTimeModeLiteral(String value) {\n        this.value = value;\n    }\n    \n    public String value() {\n        return value;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 9. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/util/RecentQuotePriceChangeList.java\nRead the current file first, then replace CDI annotations with Spring. The key pattern is:\n- Replace @ApplicationScoped with @Service\n- Replace @Inject Event with @Autowired ApplicationEventPublisher (or remove the event firing if it's just cosmetic)\n- Replace jakarta.enterprise imports with Spring imports\n\nRead this file first to see its current content, then rewrite it.\n\nWrite ALL these files using the Write tool. Read the files that need inspection first."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_019ZkhVWHwTgakqVXrTzAG4D","session_id":"0a2ab8cf-d9b3-4fb3-875c-ac24a464972f","uuid":"d70e69c8-c45e-4aa7-adab-2f787f356cbe"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You need to REWRITE the following Java service files in-place at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_2/output to migrate from Quarkus CDI to Spring Boot. Use the Read tool to read each file first, then use the Write tool to write the migrated version.\n\nREAD EACH FILE BEFORE WRITING.\n\n## 1. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/TradeSLSBBean.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service` and add `@Primary`\n- Replace `@Inject EntityManager` with `@PersistenceContext EntityManager`\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` with `org.springframework.stereotype.Service`\n- Replace `jakarta.inject.Inject` with `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n- Replace `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n- Remove CDI qualifier annotations (@Default, @TradeEJB, @RuntimeMode, @Trace)\n- Remove `jakarta.enterprise.event.Event` and `@MarketSummaryUpdate` event, replace with nothing (just remove event firing)\n- Remove `@Any Instance<TradeServices>` usage - replace with direct @Autowired\n- Keep the `@Transactional` annotation on class\n- Keep all business logic unchanged\n\n## 2. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/MarketSummarySingleton.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service`\n- Replace `@Inject EntityManager` with `@PersistenceContext EntityManager` \n- Replace `io.quarkus.scheduler.Scheduled` with `org.springframework.scheduling.annotation.Scheduled`\n- Change `@Scheduled(every = \"20s\")` to `@Scheduled(fixedRate = 20000)`\n- Remove CDI `Event<String>` and `@MarketSummaryUpdate` - just remove the event firing lines\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise` imports with Spring imports\n- Replace `jakarta.inject.Inject` with `@Autowired`\n\n## 3. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/session2direct/DirectSLSBBean.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service(\"directSLSBBean\")`\n- Remove `@TradeSession2Direct`, `@RuntimeMode`, `@Trace` annotations\n- Replace `@Inject @TradeJDBC TradeServices tradeDirect` with `@Autowired @Qualifier(\"tradeDirect\") TradeServices tradeDirect`\n- Replace `@Inject AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter` with `@Autowired`\n- Replace `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n- Replace all `jakarta.enterprise` and `jakarta.inject` imports with Spring imports\n- Add `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier;`\n\n## 4. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrder.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@Dependent` with `@Component` and `@Scope(\"prototype\")`\n- Remove CDI `@Any Instance<TradeServices>` - replace constructor with simple @Autowired TradeServices\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise` and `jakarta.inject` imports with Spring imports\n- Add `import org.springframework.context.annotation.Scope;`\n- Change constructor to use @Autowired TradeServices directly (no Instance/select pattern)\n\n## 5. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@RequestScoped` with `@Service`\n- Remove `@VirtualThreads` and `io.quarkus.virtual.threads.VirtualThreads` import\n- Replace `@Inject ExecutorService` with a simple `java.util.concurrent.Executors.newCachedThreadPool()` field\n- Replace `@Inject AsyncScheduledOrder` with `@Autowired`\n- Replace all `jakarta` imports with Spring imports\n\n## 6. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/AsyncOrderSubmitter.java\nRead first, then migrate similarly to AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.\n\n## 7. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/AsyncOrder.java\nRead first, then migrate similarly to AsyncScheduledOrder.\n\nWrite ALL files using the Write tool."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014E5cqqH4NQFf1TiQASdPng","session_id":"0a2ab8cf-d9b3-4fb3-875c-ac24a464972f","uuid":"8ec59872-3c57-4138-a342-07ee98dba940"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"You need to REWRITE the following Java files in-place at /home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__daytrader__quarkus__spring/run_2/output to migrate from Quarkus CDI to Spring Boot. Use the Read tool to read each file first, then use the Write tool to write the migrated version.\n\nREAD EACH FILE BEFORE WRITING. Preserve all business logic.\n\n## 1. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/TradeDirect.java\nThis is the most complex file. Key changes:\n- Replace `@Dependent` with `@Service(\"tradeDirect\")` and add `@Scope(\"prototype\")`\n- Remove `@TradeJDBC`, `@RuntimeMode(\"Direct (JDBC)\")`, `@Trace` annotations\n- Replace `@Inject private DataSource datasource` with `@Autowired private DataSource datasource`\n- REMOVE `@Inject private UserTransaction txn` entirely. Remove the `import jakarta.transaction.UserTransaction;`\n- REMOVE `import io.quarkus.narayana.jta.QuarkusTransaction;`\n- Replace `@Inject RecentQuotePriceChangeList` with `@Autowired`\n- Replace `@Inject AsyncOrderSubmitter` with `@Autowired`\n- Replace `@Inject @MarketSummaryUpdate Event<String> mkSummaryUpdateEvent` with NOTHING (remove the field)\n- Replace `@Inject MessageProducerService messageProducer` with `@Autowired`\n- In the `buy()` method: Replace `txn.begin()` / `txn.commit()` / `txn.rollback()` with setting `conn.setAutoCommit(false)` and using `conn.commit()` / `conn.rollback()`. Set `inGlobalTxn = false` where `txn.begin()` was.\n- In the `sell()` method: Same as buy - remove txn usage, use connection-level transactions\n- Remove `mkSummaryUpdateEvent.fireAsync(...)` calls\n- Replace all `jakarta.enterprise`, `jakarta.inject` imports with Spring imports\n- Add `import org.springframework.stereotype.Service;` and `import org.springframework.context.annotation.Scope;` and `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired;`\n- Keep `import javax.sql.DataSource;` (this is standard Java)\n- Keep `import jakarta.annotation.Resource;` only if needed, otherwise remove\n- Remove `import jakarta.annotation.Resource;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.enterprise.context.Dependent;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.enterprise.event.Event;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.enterprise.event.NotificationOptions;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.inject.Inject;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.transaction.UserTransaction;`\n- Remove `import jakarta.validation.constraints.NotNull;`\n\nFor the buy/sell transaction handling, change the pattern from:\n```java\nif (!inSession && orderProcessingMode == TradeConfig.ASYNCH_2PHASE) {\n    txn.begin();\n    setInGlobalTxn(true);\n}\n```\nTo:\n```java\n// 2-phase not supported in Spring - use connection-level transactions\n```\nAnd remove:\n```java\nif (getInGlobalTxn()) {\n    txn.commit();\n    setInGlobalTxn(false);\n}\n```\nReplace with:\n```java\ncommit(conn);\n```\nSimilarly for rollback.\n\n## 2. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/impl/direct/TradeDirectDBUtils.java\nKey changes:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service`\n- Replace `@Inject AgroalDataSource datasource` with `@Autowired DataSource datasource`\n- Remove `import io.agroal.api.AgroalDataSource;`\n- Replace `@Inject @TradeJDBC TradeServices ts` with `@Autowired @Qualifier(\"tradeDirect\") TradeServices ts`\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped` with `org.springframework.stereotype.Service`\n- Replace `jakarta.inject.Inject` with `org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Autowired`\n- Add `import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Qualifier;`\n\n## 3. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/messaging/MessageProducerService.java\nReplace SmallRye Reactive Messaging with Spring ApplicationEventPublisher:\n```java\npackage com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.messaging;\n\nimport java.math.BigDecimal;\n\nimport org.springframework.context.ApplicationEventPublisher;\nimport org.springframework.stereotype.Service;\n\nimport com.ibm.websphere.samples.daytrader.util.Log;\n\n@Service\npublic class MessageProducerService {\n\n    private final ApplicationEventPublisher eventPublisher;\n\n    public MessageProducerService(ApplicationEventPublisher eventPublisher) {\n        this.eventPublisher = eventPublisher;\n    }\n\n    public void queueOrderForProcessing(Integer orderID, boolean twoPhase) {\n        OrderMessage message = OrderMessage.newOrder(orderID, twoPhase);\n        Log.trace(\"MessageProducerService:queueOrderForProcessing - sending order \" + orderID);\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(message);\n    }\n\n    public void sendBrokerPing(String text) {\n        OrderMessage message = OrderMessage.ping(text);\n        Log.trace(\"MessageProducerService:sendBrokerPing - sending ping\");\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(message);\n    }\n\n    public void publishQuoteUpdate(String symbol, BigDecimal newPrice, BigDecimal oldPrice) {\n        QuoteUpdateMessage message = QuoteUpdateMessage.quoteUpdate(symbol, newPrice, oldPrice);\n        Log.trace(\"MessageProducerService:publishQuoteUpdate - publishing update for \" + symbol);\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(message);\n    }\n\n    public void publishQuotePriceChange(String symbol, String company, BigDecimal price,\n            BigDecimal oldPrice, BigDecimal open, BigDecimal low, BigDecimal high,\n            double volume, BigDecimal changeFactor, double sharesTraded) {\n        QuoteUpdateMessage message = QuoteUpdateMessage.quoteUpdate(symbol, price, oldPrice);\n        message.setCompany(company);\n        message.setOpen(open);\n        message.setLow(low);\n        message.setHigh(high);\n        message.setVolume(volume);\n        message.setChangeFactor(changeFactor);\n        message.setSharesTraded(sharesTraded);\n        Log.trace(\"MessageProducerService:publishQuotePriceChange - publishing update for \" + symbol);\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(message);\n    }\n\n    public void sendStreamerPing(String text) {\n        QuoteUpdateMessage message = QuoteUpdateMessage.ping(text);\n        Log.trace(\"MessageProducerService:sendStreamerPing - sending ping\");\n        eventPublisher.publishEvent(message);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 4. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTBroker3MDB.java\nReplace @Incoming with Spring @EventListener:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service`\n- Replace `@Incoming(\"trade-broker-queue\")` with `@EventListener`\n- Replace `jakarta.transaction.Transactional` with `org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional`\n- Remove `org.eclipse.microprofile.reactive.messaging.Incoming`\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise` and `jakarta.inject` imports with Spring imports\n- Keep @PostConstruct (use `jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct`)\n\n## 5. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/mdb/DTStreamer3MDB.java\nSame pattern as DTBroker3MDB:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Service`\n- Replace `@Incoming(\"trade-streamer-topic\")` with `@EventListener`\n- Remove MicroProfile imports\n\n## 6. src/main/java/com/ibm/websphere/samples/daytrader/startup/DatabasePopulator.java\nRead first, then:\n- Replace `@ApplicationScoped` with `@Component`\n- Replace `@Inject EntityManager` with `@PersistenceContext EntityManager`\n- Replace `@ConfigProperty(name = \"trade.db.populate.on.startup\")` with `@Value(\"${trade.db.populate.on.startup:true}\")`\n- Replace `void onStart(@Observes StartupEvent ev)` with `@EventListener(ApplicationReadyEvent.class) public void onStart()`\n- Remove `io.quarkus.runtime.StartupEvent` import, add `org.springframework.boot.context.event.ApplicationReadyEvent` and `org.springframework.context.event.EventListener`\n- Replace `jakarta.enterprise` imports with Spring imports\n\nWrite ALL files completely using the Write tool."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01XF3hCf7peknkWsRWZkLDyd","session_id":"0a2ab8cf-d9b3-4fb3-875c-ac24a464972f","uuid":"638469f0-e98a-4846-b447-194a47ae71b9"}
