ID, boolean twoPhase) {\n    39→    asyncOrder.setProperties(orderID,twoPhase);\n    40→    // MIGRATION: Use CompletableFuture with delay instead of scheduled executor\n    41→    return CompletableFuture.runAsync(() -> {\n    42→      try {\n    43→        TimeUnit.MILLISECONDS.sleep(500);\n    44→        asyncOrder.run();\n    45→      } catch (InterruptedException e) {\n    46→        Thread.currentThread().interrupt();\n    47→      }\n    48→    }, executorService);\n    49→  }\n    50→}\n    51→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014E5cqqH4NQFf1TiQASdPng","session_id":"0a2ab8cf-d9b3-4fb3-875c-ac24a464972f","uuid":"0268a22a-041b-4dc6-aea8-57beb0f1f7b9"}
