{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01RQ34qTzJqHLe46kzKbxhoK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Migration is complete. Here's the full report:\n\n---\n\n### Migration Summary\n\n**Frameworks:** Quarkus 3.17.0 -> Spring Boot 3.2.5\n**Overall Outcome:** SUCCESS - Application builds, runs, and passes all 10/10 smoke tests\n\n**High-level actions performed:**\n1. Rewrote `pom.xml` from Quarkus BOM to Spring Boot parent\n2. Created Spring Boot main application class with `@SpringBootApplication`\n3. Migrated 4 REST resources from JAX-RS to Spring MVC (`@RestController`)\n4. Migrated 12 CDI beans to Spring beans (`@Service`, `@Component`)\n5. Migrated messaging from SmallRye Reactive Messaging to Spring `ApplicationEventPublisher`\n6. Simplified 7 CDI qualifier annotations to plain Java annotations\n7. Resolved 2 circular dependency issues using `@Lazy`\n8. Updated Dockerfile for Spring Boot JAR execution\n9. Generated comprehensive smoke test suite\n\n### File Tree\n\n```\nModified:\n- pom.xml: Spring Boot 3.2.5 parent, all Spring Boot dependencies\n- src/main/resources/application.properties: Spring Boot configuration format\n- Dockerfile: Spring Boot JAR build and execution\n- src/main/java/.../jaxrs/TradeResource.java: JAX-RS -> Spring MVC @RestController\n- src/main/java/.../jaxrs/QuoteResource.java: JAX-RS -> Spring MVC @RestController\n- src/main/java/.../jaxrs/MessagingResource.java: JAX-RS -> Spring MVC @RestController\n- src/main/java/.../web/TradeAppResource.java: JAX-RS -> Spring MVC @RestController\n- src/main/java/.../impl/ejb3/TradeSLSBBean.java: CDI -> Spring @Service @Primary\n- src/main/java/.../impl/ejb3/MarketSummarySingleton.java: CDI -> Spring @Service\n- src/main/java/.../impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrder.java: CDI -> Spring @Component @Lazy\n- src/main/java/.../impl/ejb3/AsyncScheduledOrderSubmitter.java: CDI -> Spring @Service\n- src/main/java/.../impl/session2direct/DirectSLSBBea